#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.45:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga"
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 45. Paññavantasutta → paññavasuttaṃ (bj) | paññavā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Paññavantasutta"
msgstr "45. Wise"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.45:1.1"
msgid "“‘Paññavā aneḷamūgo, paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir they speak of a person who is ‘wise, no idiot’."

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti?"
msgstr "How is a person who is wise, no idiot defined?”"

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘paññavā "
"aneḷamūgo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, they’re called wise, no idiot because they’ve developed and "
"cultivated the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.5"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.6"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘"
"paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They’re called wise, no idiot because they’ve developed and cultivated these "
"seven awakening factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.45:1.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
